Package: libswitchboard-2.0-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libswitchboard-2.0-0 (= ${binary:Version}),
         gir1.2-switchboard-2.0 (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Switchboard Modular Settings Hub - development files
 The Switchboard library is the central library to create plugs.
 .
 This package contains the header and development files which are
 needed for building Switchboard plugs.

Package: gir1.2-switchboard-2.0
Section: introspection
Architecture: any
Depends: libswitchboard-2.0-0 (= ${binary:Version}),
         ${misc:Depends},
         ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${gir:Depends}
Description: Switchboard Modular Settings Hub - gir bindings
 The Switchboard library is the central library to create plugs.
 .
 This package can be used by other packages using the GIRepository format to
 generate dynamic bindings.

